agrave;y v&agrave; nh&igrave;n lại th&igrave; h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh l&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;i của Th&eacute;p Xanh Nam Định l&agrave; ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n xứng đ&aacute;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-87978\" id=\"attachment_87978\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72.jpg 2560w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-300x200.jpg 300w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-696x464.jpg 696w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-630x420.jpg 630w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1260x840.jpg 1260w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-1920x1280.jpg 1920w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72-310x207.jpg 310w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573523083432_937ae91be6155d17a4daa97e99105e72