agrave; chỉ c&oacute; một lần mất ng&ocirc;i đầu bảng v&agrave;o tay đối thủ. Thầy tr&ograve; HLV Vũ Hồng Việt cũng kh&ocirc;ng phải chờ đợi l&acirc;u để đ&ograve;i lại ng&ocirc;i đầu. Nhiều qu&atilde;ng thời gian, đội b&oacute;ng n&agrave;y cũng thi đấu bất ổn, nhưng c&aacute;c đối thủ b&aacute;m đuổi cũng kh&ocirc;ng thể tận dụng lợi thế so&aacute;n ng&ocirc;i của Th&eacute;p Xanh Nam Định.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004.jpg 2560w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-300x200.jpg 300w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-768x512.jpg 768w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-696x464.jpg 696w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1392x928.jpg 1392w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1068x712.jpg 1068w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-630x420.jpg 630w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1260x840.jpg 1260w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_49de6663b773f91f2f779ad7539d5004-1920x1280.jpg 1920w, https://vpf.vn/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/z5573471463436_